sub_title: OBC desk at Wings on Board
summary:
3 years of experience in Customer Service within the Tourism & Travel industry. I pride myself on my efficiency, problem-solving skills, and my ability to adjust to different communication styles and cultures. 
Though most of my experience was handling the Israeli market, I also have experience with customers in the USA, UK and Dutch markets.
I consider myself to be a creative person, which is a skill I applied in the past for my work as content editor and in customer service. I prefer working in an office environment, but consider my creative skills to be an advantage I bring to any workspace.
